import useStyles from './useStyles';
import { Card, CardMedia, CardContent, Typography, CardActions, Button, Grid } from '@material-ui/core';

const Home = (): JSX.Element => {
    const { root, card } = useStyles();
    const cards = [
            {
                cardImg: 'https://airportshuttle0.s3.amazonaws.com/airport-shuttle02.jpeg',
                title: 'Unconfirmed Reservations',
                content: 'Reservations waiting for confirmation!',
                number: 0,
            }, {
                cardImg: 'https://airportshuttle0.s3.amazonaws.com/money.jpeg',
                title: 'Debt',
                content: 'clients owe you moeny!!',
                number: 0,
            }
        ]
    return (
    <>
        <Grid container spacing={3} justifyContent="space-evenly" alignItems="center" className={root}>
            <Card className={card}>
                <CardMedia
                    component="img"
                    height="140"
                    image="https://airportshuttle0.s3.amazonaws.com/airport-shuttle02.jpeg"
                    alt="Debt"
                />
                <CardContent style={{ backgroundColor:'#2F4F4F' }}>
                    <Typography gutterBottom variant="h5" component="div">
                        Unconfirmed Reservations
                    </Typography>
                    <Typography variant="body2">
                        50 Reservations waiting for confirmation!
                    </Typography>
                </CardContent>
                <CardActions style={{ backgroundColor:'#A9A9A9' }}>
                    <Button size="large">Show</Button>
                </CardActions>
            </Card>
            <Card className={card}>
                <CardMedia
                    component="img"
                    height="140"
                    image="https://airportshuttle0.s3.amazonaws.com/money.jpeg"
                    alt="Debt"
                />
                <CardContent style={{ backgroundColor:'#2F4F4F', minWidth: 282.833 }}>
                    <Typography gutterBottom variant="h5" component="div">
                        Debt
                    </Typography>
                    <Typography variant="body2">
                        50 clients owe you moeny!
                    </Typography>
                </CardContent>
                <CardActions style={{ backgroundColor:'#A9A9A9' }}>
                    <Button size="large">Show</Button>
                </CardActions>
            </Card>
        </Grid>
    </>
    );
};

export default Home;
